      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required)</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1709224869059-x200.jpg",
